name: CryptoNinja #26
description: This is the strongest Member of the CryptozukiClan. He can control the Dead with his CryptoPiercings. The only thing he have to do is to pierce the Body of the Victim. He can also shoot gravityWaves. He is the Head of the CryptozukiClan but CryptoPunk #22 is the true Chief of them. Noone knows who Cryptopunk #22 is. #26 is the right hand of #22.
